  <brief_title>Use of White Granulated Sugar on Wounds</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomised Controlled Trial to Investigate the Clinical and Cost-effectiveness of White Granulated Sugar Dressing Compared With Standard Treatment in the Management of Exudating Wounds With Parallel Economic Evaluation</official_title>
